content.data: The S2M Center comes with thirteen predefined reports, simply select the report from the sidebar you would like to view.

Material Summary -   Material summary that groups the sheets used in this run by the material name, than provides a breakout of the sheet sizes used. 
 
 
 Part Labels (Opt)  - Part labels (for optimized parts) for Avery label style 5366. 
 
 
 Part Labels (Opt)  - Part labels (for optimized parts) with enlarged bar-code field for Avery label style 4013.
